title: Did Trump come as a photographer in 1990 to power and build a wall?
subtitle: In 2017, there was renewed interest in social media with a 27-year-old Peter Cooper comedian tape.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In July 1990, a comic strip in Heffy Metal presented a controversial wall in New York City, built by Donald Trump, and the populist "rebirth to power" by the next president.
